U_{N}^{S}\equiv U_{N}(C^{S},N^{S}) & =-\chi(N^{S})^{\varphi}\left(\frac{(C^{S})^{1-\gamma}}{1-\gamma}-\chi\frac{(N^{S})^{1+\varphi}}{1+\varphi}\right)^{-\xi/(1-\gamma)}
