 & =(1-\alpha)MC\frac{Y}{N}\\
\chi\frac{(N^{S})^{1+\varphi}}{(C^{S})^{1-\gamma}} & =(1-\alpha)MC\frac{N^{S}/N}{C^{S}/Y}
